node.text: Hey guys super excited to announce a collaboration with @wethelocals207 ! He did some awesome digital work on two of my pieces! My most popular poster of a silhouette of Maine with the colors based of the topographical map! As well as a new painting of my Maine makara! Shirts can be purchased through the link on their profile or on www.wethelocals.bigcartel.com ! #art #artistsoninstagram #artappreciation #artofig #appreciateart #handmadeart #headyart #oprahsbookclub #commonroots #commonrootsstudio #portland #portlandmaine #nauticalart #oceanart #shoplocal #artist #makara #maine #moose #lobster #mainemap

I'll be choosing the winner of my monthly Patron give away tomorrow. You still have time to be apart of it! All of my patrons, regardless of tier, are entered each month and the winner receives a hand drawn piece. Head over to my patreon (link in bio) and see what rewards I have to offer! 
This piece was a bit frustrating. I restarted it 3 times after putting an hour or so into each attempt. Through patience and persistence I was able to finally nail it down on my 4th try. I love the outcome, and am happy I stuck it through to the finish. I am currently working on the Timelapse video if this piece.
